      <title>Markdown入门教程（二）</title>
      <link href="/blog/2157141774.html"/>
      <url>/blog/2157141774.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2><span id="一-前言">一、前言</span></h2><blockquote><p><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/markdown/3245829?fr=aladdin">Markdown</a> 是一种轻量级标记语言，它允许使用易读易写的<strong>纯文本</strong>格式编写文档。Markdown 语言在2004年由 <strong>约翰・格鲁伯</strong> 创建，用它编写的文档后缀为 <code>.md</code> 或 <code>.markdown</code> 。</p></blockquote><h2><span id="二-应用场景">二、应用场景</span></h2><blockquote><p>Markdown 编写的文档可以导出 HTML 、Word、图像、PDF、Epub 等多种格式的文档。<br>当前许多网站都广泛使用 Markdown 来撰写帮助文档或是用于论坛上发表消息。</p></blockquote><h2><span id="三-语法介绍">三、语法介绍</span></h2><h3><span id="1-标题标记">1、标题标记</span></h3><ul><li>使用 = 和 - 标记一级和二级标题</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown">这是一级标题==========这是二级标题<span class="token hr punctuation">----------</span></code></pre><ul><li>使用 # 号标记，可表示 1-6 级标题</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">#</span> 一级标题</span><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">##</span> 二级标题</span><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">###</span> 三级标题</span><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">####</span> 四级标题</span><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">#####</span> 五级标题</span><span class="token title important"><span class="token punctuation">######</span> 六级标题</span></code></pre><h3><span id="2-段落标记">2、段落标记</span></h3><ul><li>使用两个以上空格+回车</li></ul><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zengnanyang/images/markdown/mk-section1.jpg" style="float: left; width: 1105px; box-shadow: none; margin: unset; border: 1.5px solid rgba(230,230,230,1); margin: 0 0 15px 0;"><ul><li>在段落的后面使用一个空行</li></ul><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zengnanyang/images/markdown/mk-section2.jpg" style="float: left; width: 1105px; box-shadow: none; margin: unset; border: 1.5px solid rgba(230,230,230,1); margin: 0 0 15px 0;"><h3><span id="3-分割标记">3、分割标记</span></h3><ul><li>在一行中用三个以上的 * 或 + 或 - 来建立一个分隔线，行内不能有其他东西</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token hr punctuation">******</span>++++++<span class="token hr punctuation">------</span></code></pre><ul><li>在 * 或 - 中间插入空格</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token hr punctuation">* * *</span><span class="token hr punctuation">- - -</span></code></pre><h3><span id="4-文本标记">4、文本标记</span></h3><ul><li>斜体：在文本的两端各加一个 * 或 _</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token italic"><span class="token punctuation">*</span>斜体文本<span class="token punctuation">*</span></span><span class="token italic"><span class="token punctuation">_</span>斜体文本<span class="token punctuation">_</span></span></code></pre><ul><li>粗体：在文本的两端各加两个 * 或 _</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token bold"><span class="token punctuation">**</span>粗体文本<span class="token punctuation">**</span></span><span class="token bold"><span class="token punctuation">__</span>粗体文本<span class="token punctuation">__</span></span></code></pre><ul><li>粗斜体：在文本的两端各加三个 * 或 _</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token bold"><span class="token punctuation">**</span>*粗斜体文本<span class="token punctuation">**</span></span>*<span class="token bold"><span class="token punctuation">__</span>_粗斜体文本<span class="token punctuation">__</span></span>_</code></pre><ul><li>删除线：在文字的两端加上两个波浪线~~</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown">~~删除线~~</code></pre><ul><li>下划线：使用HTML的<u></u>标签</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>u</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>下划线<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>u</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>脚注：格式是<code>[^要脚注的对象]</code></li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token url-reference url"><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token variable">^要脚注的对象</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> 这是脚注的格式。</span></code></pre><h3><span id="5-列表标记">5、列表标记</span></h3><ul><li>无序列表：以 * 或 + 或 - 开头，符号与内容间有一个空格</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token list punctuation">*</span> 无序列表方式一<span class="token list punctuation">+</span> 无序列表方式二<span class="token list punctuation">-</span> 无序列表方式三</code></pre><ul><li>有序列表：以数字加上 . 号用来表示有序列表</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token list punctuation">1.</span> 有序列表1<span class="token list punctuation">2.</span> 有序列表2</code></pre><ul><li>列表嵌套：在子列表中的选项前面添加四个空格即可</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token list punctuation">1.</span> 有序列表1<span class="token code keyword">    * 无序列表1</span><span class="token code keyword">    * 无序列表2</span><span class="token list punctuation">2.</span> 有序列表2<span class="token code keyword">    - 无序列表3</span></code></pre><h3><span id="6-区块标记">6、区块标记</span></h3><ul><li>基本语法：段落开头使用 &gt; 符号 ，然后后面紧跟一个空格符号</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token blockquote punctuation">></span> 区块一<span class="token blockquote punctuation">></span> 区块二</code></pre><ul><li>区块嵌套：一个 &gt; 符号是最外层，两个 &gt; 符号是第一层嵌套，以此类推</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token blockquote punctuation">></span> 一层区块<span class="token blockquote punctuation">> ></span> 二层区块...</code></pre><h3><span id="7-代码标记">7、代码标记</span></h3><ul><li>代码高亮：用  “<code>" 和 "</code>“ 将需要高亮的代码括起来</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown"><span class="token code keyword">`Hexo`</span></code></pre><ul><li>代码块：在段落前使用 Tab 键，效果如下图：</li></ul><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zengnanyang/images/markdown/mk-codeblockjpg.jpg" style="float: left; width: 1105px; box-shadow: none; margin: unset; border: 1.5px solid rgba(230,230,230,1); margin: 0 0 15px 0;"><h3><span id="8-链接">8、链接</span></h3><ul><li>普通链接：<a href="%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80">链接名称</a>  或者 &lt;链接地址&gt;</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown">这是一个链接 <span class="token url">[百度](www.baidu.com)</span>或者<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>www.baidu.com</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>高级链接：通过变量来设置一个链接，在文档末尾进行赋值</li></ul><pre class=" language-markdown"><code class="language-markdown">链接用 baidu 作为网址变量 <span class="token url">[百度][<span class="token variable">baidu</span>]</span><span class="token url-reference url"><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token variable">baidu</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> www.baidu.com</span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
